"integration.hook_desc_claude" = "»Install Automatically« writes three hooks into ~/.claude/settings.json: PreToolUse (sends »busy«), Notification (sends »waiting« when Claude needs your input), and Stop (sends »done«). The exact commands are shown in the snippet below. Existing hooks from other apps are not affected.";
"integration.hook_desc_codex" = "»Install Automatically« sets the onStart (sends »busy«) and onFinish (sends »done«) keys in ~/.codex/config.json. Codex has no notification hook — the waiting state is not available for Codex. Other settings in that file are not affected.";
